trans-unit.source: Provides properties for getting information about the computer's memory, loaded assemblies, name, and operating system.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder egenskaper for å få informasjon om datamaskinens minne, innlastede samlinger, navnet og operativsystemet.

trans-unit.source: The properties exposed by the `My.Computer.Info` object return information about the computer from which the application is deployed, as determined at run time.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapene som vises i den `My.Computer.Info` objekt returneres informasjon om datamaskinen som distribueres applikasjonen, som under kjøring.

trans-unit.source: Typically, this data differs from what was available on the development computer.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis disse dataene er forskjellig fra som var tilgjengelig på utviklingsdatamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Devices.ComputerInfo"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Devices.ComputerInfo"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the total amount of free physical memory for the computer.
trans-unit.target: Henter den totale mengden ledig fysisk minne for datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: The `My.Computer.Info.AvailablePhysicalMemory` property requires Windows XP, Windows 2000 Professional, Windows Server 2003, Windows 2000 Server, or Windows Vista.
trans-unit.target: Den `My.Computer.Info.AvailablePhysicalMemory` egenskapen krever Windows XP, Windows 2000 Professional, Windows Server 2003, Windows 2000 Server eller Windows Vista.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_ULong" name="ULong" href=""></xref> containing the number of bytes of free physical memory for the computer.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_ULong" name="ULong" href=""> </xref> som inneholder antall byte ledig fysisk minne for datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: The application cannot obtain the memory status.
trans-unit.target: Programmet kan ikke hente minnestatus for.

trans-unit.source: Gets the total amount of the computer's free virtual address space.
trans-unit.target: Henter den totale mengden datamaskinens gratis virtuelt adresseområde.

trans-unit.source: The `My.Computer.Info.AvailableVirtualMemory` property requires Windows XP, Windows 2000 Professional, Windows Server 2003, Windows 2000 Server, or Windows Vista.
trans-unit.target: Den `My.Computer.Info.AvailableVirtualMemory` egenskapen krever Windows XP, Windows 2000 Professional, Windows Server 2003, Windows 2000 Server eller Windows Vista.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_ULong" name="ULong" href=""></xref> containing the number of bytes of the computer's free virtual address space.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_ULong" name="ULong" href=""> </xref> som inneholder antall byte datamaskinens gratis virtuelt adresseområde.

trans-unit.source: The application cannot obtain the memory status.
trans-unit.target: Programmet kan ikke hente minnestatus for.

trans-unit.source: Gets the current UI culture installed with the operating system.
trans-unit.target: Henter gjeldende brukergrensesnittkultur installert med operativsystemet.

trans-unit.source: The `My.Computer.Info.InstalledUICulture` property has the same behavior as the <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InstalledUICulture%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den `My.Computer.Info.InstalledUICulture` egenskapen har på samme måte som den <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InstalledUICulture%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InstalledUICulture%2A>

trans-unit.source: In a localized operating system, such as Japanese Windows 2000 Professional, this property returns the culture of the operating system.
trans-unit.target: I en lokalisert operativsystem, for eksempel japansk Windows 2000 Professional returnerer egenskapen kulturen av operativsystemet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> object represents the UI culture installed on the computer.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>objektet representerer UI-språket som er installert på datamaskinen.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: Gets the full operating system name.
trans-unit.target: Henter navnet hele operativsystem.

trans-unit.source: This property returns detailed information about the operating system name if Windows Management Instrumentation (WMI) is installed on the computer.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen returnerer detaljert informasjon om navnet operativsystemet Hvis Windows Management Instrumentation (WMI) er installert på datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, this property returns the same string as the `My.Computer.Info.OSPlatform` property, which provides less detailed information than WMI can provide.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ikke, denne returnerer samme strengen som den `My.Computer.Info.OSPlatform` egenskap, som gir mindre detaljert informasjon enn WMI kan tilby.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_String" name="String" href=""></xref> containing the operating-system name.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_String" name="String" href=""> </xref> som inneholder navnet på operativsystemet.

trans-unit.source: The calling code does not have full trust.
trans-unit.target: Kall koden har ikke fullstendig klarering.

trans-unit.source: Gets the platform identifier for the operating system of the computer.
trans-unit.target: Henter plattformen identifikatoren for operativsystemet på datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: The `My.Computer.Info.OSPlatform` property provides functionality similar to the <xref:System.OperatingSystem.Platform%2A> property of the object returned by the <xref:System.Environment.OSVersion%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den `My.Computer.Info.OSPlatform` egenskapen gir funksjonalitet som er lik den <xref:System.OperatingSystem.Platform%2A>for objektet som returneres av den <xref:System.Environment.OSVersion%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Environment.OSVersion%2A> </xref:System.OperatingSystem.Platform%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_String" name="String" href=""></xref> containing the platform identifier for the operating system of the computer, chosen from the member names of the <xref href="System.PlatformID"></xref> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_String" name="String" href=""> </xref> som inneholder plattformen identifikatoren for operativsystemet på datamaskinen, velges fra medlemsnavnene for den <xref href="System.PlatformID"> </xref> opplisting.

trans-unit.source: The application cannot obtain the operating-system platform information.
trans-unit.target: Programmet kan ikke hente informasjonen operativsystemet plattformen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the version of the computer's operating system.
trans-unit.target: Henter versjonen av operativsystemet på datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: The `My.Computer.Info.OSVersion` property formats the version as "major.minor.build.revision".
trans-unit.target: Den `My.Computer.Info.OSVersion` egenskapen formaterer versjonen som "major.minor.build.revision".

trans-unit.source: The `My.Computer.Info.OSVersion` property provides functionality similar to the <xref:System.OperatingSystem.Version%2A> property of the object returned by the <xref:System.Environment.OSVersion%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den `My.Computer.Info.OSVersion` egenskapen gir funksjonalitet som er lik den <xref:System.OperatingSystem.Version%2A>for objektet som returneres av den <xref:System.Environment.OSVersion%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Environment.OSVersion%2A> </xref:System.OperatingSystem.Version%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_String" name="String" href=""></xref> containing the current version number of the operating system.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_String" name="String" href=""> </xref> som inneholder gjeldende versjonsnummer av operativsystemet.

trans-unit.source: The application cannot obtain the operating-system version information.
trans-unit.target: Programmet kan ikke hente operativsystemet versjonsinformasjonen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the total amount of physical memory for the computer.
trans-unit.target: Henter den totale mengden fysisk minne for datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: The `My.Computer.Info.TotalPhysicalMemory` property requires Windows XP, Windows 2000 Professional, Windows Server 2003, Windows 2000 Server, or Windows Vista..
trans-unit.target: Den `My.Computer.Info.TotalPhysicalMemory` egenskapen krever Windows XP, Windows 2000 Professional, Windows Server 2003, Windows 2000 Server eller Windows Vista..

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_ULong" name="ULong" href=""></xref> containing the number of bytes of physical memory for the computer.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_ULong" name="ULong" href=""> </xref> som inneholder antall byte fysisk minne for datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: The application cannot obtain the memory status.
trans-unit.target: Programmet kan ikke hente minnestatus for.

trans-unit.source: Gets the total amount of virtual address space available for the computer.
trans-unit.target: Henter den totale mengden tilgjengelig virtuelt adresseområde for datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: The `My.Computer.Info.TotalVirtualMemory` property requires Windows XP, Windows 2000 Professional, Windows Server 2003, Windows 2000 Server, or Windows Vista..
trans-unit.target: Den `My.Computer.Info.TotalVirtualMemory` egenskapen krever Windows XP, Windows 2000 Professional, Windows Server 2003, Windows 2000 Server eller Windows Vista..

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_ULong" name="ULong" href=""></xref> containing the number of bytes of virtual address space available for the computer.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_ULong" name="ULong" href=""> </xref> som inneholder antall byte av virtuelt adresseområde for datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: The application cannot obtain the memory status.
trans-unit.target: Programmet kan ikke hente minnestatus for.
